title: Advances in Bioengineering - Pier Andrea Serra
description:
Advances in Bioengineering - Pier Andrea Serra (AvE4EvA, 2015).pdf

ISBN-10 953-51-2141-3
ISBN-13 978-953-51-2141-1

The technological approach and the high level of innovation make bioengineering extremely dynamic and this forces researchers to continuous updating. It involves the publication of the results of the latest scientific research.

This book covers a wide range of aspects and issues related to advances in bioengineering research with a particular focus on innovative technologies and applications. The book consists of 13 scientific contributions divided in four sections:
Materials Science; Biosensors. Electronics and Telemetry; Light Therapy; Computing and Analysis Techniques
